data.description: Beautiful home within walking distance of school has spacious layout, brick fireplace, & high ceilings! Lot of updates: laminate flooring throughout the entire home, entire interior has been repainted, stainless steel appliances, lighting, custom kitchen cabinets, solid granite counter tops, faucets, etc. AC unit have been recently maintained. Lot of windows for natural lighting. primary suite has double vanity. Fully renovated shower with quartz bench to relax the day away in. Two walk-in closets & toilet room is separate. The roof was replaced in 2021. No Carpet!! French doors to backyard give the home a vast feel. Many large mature tree. Large backyard!!
